# This file ensures the assets/dist/ directory is tracked in Git.
#
# Built React assets (wizard.HASH.js, wizard.HASH.css, manifest.json) live here.
# They are produced by `pnpm --filter @growth-ops/wizard build` and copied via
# scripts/build-plugin.{sh,ps1} (Step 3F).
#
# For Step 3E: copy apps/wizard/dist/* into this directory manually one time
# to see the wizard render. The automated script lands in Step 3F.
